data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET due to BUYER FINANCING! Nice home, looking for its Perfect Buyer. At 3,417 sq ft this 6 bed, 3.5 bath is perfect for a large family. The  kitchen has tons of storage with updated cabinets and stone countertops. It opens into the living space so you can easily watch the kids or not miss any special plays of the big game while you're cooking. Serve formal meals in the dining room or the space can be used as a beautiful office or multi-functional area. No need to worry about carpet downstairs as the main level has beautiful hardwood floors and easy to clean tile. Relax in your spacious main suite after a long day. The main bath has double vanities, a large soaking tub, a separate shower, and a walk in closet. Everyone has their own space with 4 additional bedrooms upstairs and 1 in the finished basement. Downstairs is perfect for multi-generational families and/or entertaining. Outside there's a deck ideal for grilling, a nice yard, & an enclosed sunroom. Tour it today!
